							<p>If you see something not so nice, please, <a href="http://www.seriouseats.com/contact?selected=flag&url=http://www.seriouseats.com/2008/07/america-regional-hot-dog-styles-coneys-half-smokes-reds-whites.html">report an inappropriate comment.</a></strong></p>
						</div>
						
					
